						               													<description>Dark Knight. Caped Crusader. World&amp;rsquo;s Greatest Detective. Whatever you know him as, wherever you know him from&amp;mdash;the blockbuster movies, TV shows, video games, cartoons, or millions of comics&amp;mdash;Batman is proof you don&amp;rsquo;t need superpowers to be a superhero&amp;hellip; and the poster boy for what a bad childhood can do to you.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Millionaire Bruce Wayne was just a kid when he watched his parents get gunned down during a mugging in Gotham City. The crime would define his life, as he dedicated himself to becoming the world&amp;rsquo;s greatest weapon against crime&amp;mdash;the Batman.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Forget his Batarangs, Batmobile, or Utility Belt filled with high-tech weapons. Batman is the most feared superhero of all because he&amp;rsquo;s pushed himself to the absolute pinnacle of human achievement. He&amp;rsquo;s a brilliant detective who&amp;rsquo;s mastered fighting techniques the world&amp;rsquo;s barely heard of. An Olympic-caliber athlete with a plan for every occasion, Batman&amp;rsquo;s seemingly always five steps ahead of his foes. But in his crusade against injustice, two questions always loom: How far will he go to protect the innocent, and will he sacrifice his humanity along the way?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;2019 will be the 80th birthday for the caped crusader since his first appearance in Detective Comics #27 from 1939. So what better way to celebrate than with a new version of Batman. The 80th Anniversary miniature sees the Dark Knight leaping into action, surrounded by a cloud of bats, to instil fear into the hearts of his foes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Happy birthday, Bruce. Here&amp;rsquo;s to another Bat-Tastic 80 years!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
